name: Super Mario 64: Last Impact
overview:
Super Mario 64 Last Impact, is the best hackrom game of Super Mario 64. This game has 130 stars (80 required), 12 powerups, many new bosses, and a large variety of completely new levels. Over 4000 hours of work has finally come together.
Ready to enjoy the Super Mario 64 sequel, what you have asked so much?

Dificulty: 2/5
